data.description: Nice ranch style home with 3 bedrooms & 2 full bathrooms. You'll love the spacious front porch that owners have secured for children or pets to play. The backyard is also fully fenced and gated making it pet friendly, and has a large 24' x 20' workshop with roll up door and electricity. Inside you'll find a large living space open to the dining area and kitchen with updated appliances and large walk in pantry.  This home has great storage space with his & her closets in the master bedroom and a generous storage room off from the laundry area. The master bedroom is large enough for an office space inside and boasts an ensuite bathroom. HVAC is 4 years old, & driveway has been repaved. Home has attached carport that can be used for parking or entertainment space.
